<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink335">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi namvayi</l>
<l>ṉeyttō raṉṉa cevviya veruvai</l>
<l>kaṟpuṭai maruṅkiṟ kaṭumuṭai yārkkuṅ</l>
<l>kāṭunaṉi kaṭiya veṉpa</l>
<l>nīṭi yivaṇvarunar ceṉṟa vāṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>He is coming here to us with delay – </l>
<l>they say, very difficult is his path through the wilderness, </l>
<l>where vultures, that smell with blood, </l>
<l>feast on coarse flesh near the rocks. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
